## Kibot - Artifacts
**/Artifacts/**
kibot_errors.filter
*-erc.txt
*-drc.txt
*.log
*.ogv
# My KiCost config file with Keys on it
kicost_WITH_KEYS_DO_NOT_COMMIT.yaml

# Temporary files
*.000
*.*bak
*.bck
*.sch-bak
*.kicad_pcb-bak
*~
_autosave-*
*.tmp
*-cache.lib
*-rescue.lib
*-save.pro
*-save.kicad_pcb
