*.lck

# Netlist files (exported from Eeschema)
*.net

# Autorouter files (exported from Pcbnew)
*.dsn
*.ses

# Fabrication Outputs: gerbers / boms / etc
*.xml
*.csv

# KiBot Artifacts
**/Generated/**
LED_Dimmer-*rc.html

